    <value>Regex pattern matching the member path inside the DB.
Examples:
  .*\.messageId$  — matches any member ending in .messageId
  .*{udt:messageConfig_UDT}\.messageId$  — only inside specific UDT
Tokens: {udt:Name} matches UDT type, {childUdt:Name} matches child UDT.
Wildcards: .* (any), .+ (one or more). Anchors: ^ (start), $ (end).</value>
  </data>
  <data name="ConfigEditor_Help_Datatype" xml:space="preserve">
